<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idm68508272">
<term>anjón</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm68508272-meaning">neikvætt hlaðið atóm eða
sameind (inniheldur fleiri rafeindir en róteindir)</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp230158528">
<term>atómmassi</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp230158528-meaning">meðalmassi atóma
frumefnis, gefinn upp í atómmassaeiningum (amu)</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm20897872">
<term>atómmassaeining (amu)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm20897872-meaning">(einnig, sameinuð
atómmassaeining, u, eða Dalton, Da) massaeining sem jafngildir 1/12 af
massa 12C atóms</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp42201168">
<term>sætistala (Z)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp42201168-meaning">fjöldi róteinda í kjarna
atóms</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp1800912">
<term>katjón</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp1800912-meaning">jákvætt hlaðið atóm eða
sameind (inniheldur færri rafeindir en róteindir)</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm109251440">
<term>efnatákn</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm109251440-meaning">eins, tveggja eða
þriggja stafa skammstöfun sem notuð er til að tákna frumefni eða atóm
þess</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm103888640">
<term>Dalton (Da)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm103888640-meaning">önnur eining sem
jafngildir atómmassaeiningu</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp226765840">
<term>grunneining hleðslu</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp226765840-meaning">(einnig kölluð
einingarhleðsla) jafngildir stærð hleðslu rafeindar (e) þar sem e =
1,602 × 10−19 C</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp277782656">
<term>jón</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp277782656-meaning">rafmagnslega hlaðið atóm
eða sameind (inniheldur ójafnan fjölda róteinda og rafeinda)</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp22869776">
<term>massatala (A)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp22869776-meaning">summa fjölda nifteinda og
róteinda í kjarna atóms</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm284976">
<term>sameinuð atómmassaeining
(u)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm284976-meaning">önnur eining sem jafngildir
atómmassaeiningu</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>
